{"tid":1886624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國又跪！又做龜孫子！宣布減免對美進口商品反制關稅","createTime":"2020-02-19T04:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T08:38:39.000Z","uid":28114,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c4f8c32c46675e3dcbf92b51f2ebf0001c7ae58f","tid":1886624,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"中國宣布再減免自美國進口商品反制關稅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/9BC2DE8F-190C-40F4-AF0F-008C057ADA3A_w408_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F9BC2DE8F-190C-40F4-AF0F-008C057ADA3A_w408_r1_s.jpg&h=728be91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普總統和劉鶴副總理在白宮簽署第一階段經貿協議(2020年1月15日)<br />\n<br />\n中國當局2月18日宣布第三輪減免對美進口商品的反制關稅，涉及美國的豬肉、牛肉及大豆等696項商品。這是美中第一階段貿易協議2月14日生效後，中國採取的最具實質性的關稅減免措施。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報導，中國企業從3月2日起可向國務院關稅稅則委員會提出自美採購商品關稅減免申請，逐一審核批准後，有效期為一年。<br />\n<br />\n中國承諾未來兩年增加採購2000億美元的美國商品及服務。這次關稅減免商品包括豬肉、牛肉、大豆、液化天然氣、原油等曾被中國征收額外關稅的美國主要農業和能源產品。<br />\n<br />\n不過，自去年年底前爆發的武漢新冠病毒疫情，令人擔憂中國完成購買美國商品目標的能力。中國各地方當局為控制疫情，嚴格限制旅行及交通，令許多工廠無法開工或只能部分開工，居民也無法離家外出，嚴重影響消費。<br />\n<br />\n目前，中國的新冠病毒疫情已使7萬多人感染，1800多人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n白宮經濟顧問庫德洛這個月早些時候表示，中國國家主席習近平在最近與特朗普總統通話時確認，中國將完成雙方第一階段貿易協議的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-to-grant-tariff-exemptions-on-696-u-s-goods-to-support-purchases-20200218/5292913.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fchina-to-grant-tariff-exemptions-on-696-u-s-goods-to-support-purchases-20200218%2F5292913.html&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=c67c865c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-to-grant-tariff-exemptions-on-696-u-s-goods-to-support-purchases-20200218/5292913.html</a>"},{"pid":"230fb95eab07da2fbd721f70555d3ffa78e6ad9d","tid":1886624,"uid":28114,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hpUt4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hpUt4N.jpg&h=cf912698&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9f3b8a4153d391ef2ef676ce2bc078ccf515d53","tid":1886624,"uid":119442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"強國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033040e05758e4ff83332333a9e0f32374e781b9","tid":1886624,"uid":227271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ELsVXYP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELsVXYP.gif&h=3c8a0268&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed2e56cacc3f0304c1acfa7cb3516e7b08c0de75","tid":1886624,"uid":136735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"玩唔起又學人跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea09619ceb3b0efaa0ad344b63241541ce73b0af","tid":1886624,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"之前又吹風話因為武漢肺炎，未必能夠兌現到第一階段貿易協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果依家又冇咗呢回事，做咗龜孫子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b247a7c6d8ea321f38bc3507f80b2c9ffd027583","tid":1886624,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賣港狗共呢幾日明顯夾埋5大免費電媒，係咁loop用毒船黎spin走武漢啦！今日冚家超仲的起個狗官樣屌架佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔配合？？咁支狗呢？？！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共同支共不嬲至叻抽死人尾水白事當功積，口交部仲吓吓一涉及外國睇有位賺就話係外交事務擦存在感添！！<br />\n<br />\n但大家有<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif