,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"230fb95eab07da2fbd721f70555d3ffa78e6ad9d","tid":1886624,"uid":28114,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hpUt4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hpUt4N.jpg&h=cf912698&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d3baa55628dafe6574179dc55b08f41faec67c","tid":1886624,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f8c32c46675e3dcbf92b51f2ebf0001c7ae58f","tid":1886624,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"中國宣布再減免自美國進口商品反制關稅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/9BC2DE8F-190C-40F4-AF0F-008C057ADA3A_w408_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F9BC2DE8F-190C-40F4-AF0F-008C057ADA3A_w408_r1_s.jpg&h=728be91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普總統和劉鶴副總理在白宮簽署第一階段經貿協議(2020年1月15日)<br />\n<br />\n中國當局2月18日宣布第三輪減免對美進口商品的反制關稅，涉及美國的豬肉、牛肉及大豆等696項商品。這是美中第一階段貿易協議2月14日生效後，中國採取的最具實質性的關稅減免措施。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報導，中國企業從3月2日起可向國務院關稅稅則委員會提出自美採購商品關稅減免申請，逐一審核批准後，有效期為一年。<br />\n<br />\n中國承諾未來兩年增加採購2000億美元的美國商品及服務。這次關稅減免商品包括豬肉、牛肉、大豆、液化天然氣、原油等曾被中國征收額外關稅的美國主要農業和能源產品。<br />\n<br />\n不過，自去年年底前爆發的武漢新冠病毒疫情，令人擔憂中國完成購買美國商品目標的能力。中國各地方當局為控制疫情，嚴格限制旅行及交通，令許多工廠無法開工或只能部分開工，居民也無法離家外出，嚴重影響消費。<br />\n<br />\n目前，中國的新冠病毒疫情已使7萬多人感染，1800多人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n白宮經濟顧問庫德洛這個月早些時候表示，中國國家主席習近平在最近與特朗普總統通話時確認，中國將完成雙方第一階段貿易協議的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-to-grant-tariff-exemptions-on-696-u-s-goods-to-support-purchases-20200218/5292913.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fchina-to-grant-tariff-exemptions-on-696-u-s-goods-to-support-purchases-20200218%2F5292913.html&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=c67c865c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-to-grant-tariff-exemptions-on-696-u-s-goods-to-support-purchases-20200218/5292913.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"Tvb 夠唔夠膽播呢啲"},{"pid":"05b7c82f9612ff73e6dbbc474678d9f022134de0","tid":1886624,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56293e46d29d363c40ac385a1ebef0bb1580eed2","tid":1886624,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"共匪你好無面呀！<br />\n變成不合法管治"},{"pid":"7ca930182fcb71c1c8a416707544b416eae1f728","tid":1886624,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea9fab385d2ba6548177d45e8a8875df8ccbf81","tid":1886624,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ccf0ec9825d2821cce49cba99edcb2cd95ea68","tid":1886624,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:21:01.000Z","msg":"多鳩餘啦, 都冇人敢去買大陸貨, 減唔減都一樣要仆街!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"係減免美國入口中國嘅關稅呀"},{"pid":"ec6dfafad5a305ffe1b28cea37241f9709137126","tid":1886624,"uid":295224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:43:58.000Z","msg":"唔見棺材唔流眼淚 敗家習而家散盡家財啦 仆街!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\"